	 <h1 id="Football"><I>Football</I></h1>
	 <Strong id="Football1"> Anybody who knows me or has known me knows my immense love for soccer. Soccer as been my comfort and favourite sport for a long time now. </strong>
	 
     <p> Since childhood, I would wake up every night to watch soccer matches on television and the same continues now. It was the outcome of seeing matches that my interest grew in learning soccer as well. Little me, would learn their patterns on how to tackle, defend and hit goal by repeating the same movements as the players, who played on television. Soon, I was able to master my ability on scoring goals and the interest in football kept increasing. I even played many inter-school soccer competitions during my primary and high school. Since then, not a single day goes by when i don't play soccer. It's like a regime that I don't ever want to break. </p>
	 
	 <h1> <I>Singing </I></h1>
